# Cursor AI Rules for Goat Sales App

## Project Context
This is a Next.js application with AI voice capabilities using Vapi, Deepgram, and Pinecone.

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all new files
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions
- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer async/await over promises

## AI Behavior
- Reference docs/ for framework and architecture decisions
- Follow the GOAT framework (docs/GOAT_FRAMEWORK.md) for development process
- Check TECH_STACK.md for integration patterns
- Consider ROADMAP.md for future features

## File Organization
- Components in src/components/
- App routes in src/app/
- Utilities and integrations in src/lib/
- Documentation in docs/
